history.text: I like this because it has animals
The animals with human qualities are great, and I really enjoy how smart the film is.
do you generally watch animated movies?
Yes. I often have watch cartoons and animated movies. I have two small children. The thing about this movie is that it is great for adults and kids.
Yes, I really enjoy the plot and Judy Hopps
Judy Hopps is a very engaging character. I like that she is a rabbit and has the last name Hopps. Solid pun.

Agreed, I like that Nick -- a fox is a con artist. I feel like that is appropriate c
haracterization
This play into the idea that people are more than their stereotypes as well.
Yes, I like that there's lots of adventure too
Overall it really is a likable film.
I don't know that I like that Judy blackmails Nick though
I mean, he is a conman so it isn't like he doesn't work the system to get what he needs. But yes. Blackmail isn't very nice.
Agree, blackmail isn't the appropriate way to get what you want. However, at least Judy learns that Nick had a hard life
They come together and it really highlights the inclusive nature that the film is going for.
Yes, I like that Judy saves Nick. It's nice to see a strong female character.
And despite her blackmailing him, he stands up to Chief Bogo for her which is also nice.
it's sad that Judy ends up quitting her job though
Yes. Also that she upsets everyone with her talk about predatory biology.
worse that she ends up upsetting Nick with her comments, after they became friends
And she gets all the praise for solving the case too!
do you agree with the movie rating?

Yes. I do. The responses align
 with the rating as well.
I like that Nick doesn't abandon Judy even after he's been upset with her.
And how they work together to solve the crime and set up Assistant Mayor Bellwether!
yes, there is justice and I like that Bellwether is arrested
The ZPD shows up just in time to arrest her.
It was smart of Judy to record his confession. Again, great to see a smart female rolemodel
And for them to use the blueberries as replacement pellets.
Ginnifer Goodwin's voice and acting are great as Judy
She really does it justice
Yes. And Chief Bogo's voice acting is great too.
